116
00:09:23,071 --> 00:09:25,713
And generally, when you take something

117
00:09:25,713 --> 00:09:27,934
from a linear environment like film

118
00:09:27,934 --> 00:09:29,896
into a dynamic environment like games,

119
00:09:29,896 --> 00:09:34,319
it's not a trivial task, because those assets were created

120
00:09:34,319 --> 00:09:36,201
for very specific situations.

121
00:09:36,201 --> 00:09:39,243
And in the game, you can encounter a lot more.

122
00:09:39,691 --> 00:09:44,494
different situations for those sounds, like different distances, perspectives, angles,

123
00:09:44,494 --> 00:09:45,935
environments.

