125
00:09:51,219 --> 00:09:58,204
or weapon for players to use for many hours, right, to make it their primary experience.

126
00:09:58,204 --> 00:10:03,147
And of course, if it's just one sound in the movies, the quantity and variety just isn't

127
00:10:03,147 --> 00:10:04,788
there to support that gameplay.

128
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:08,020
So there were a lot of blanks that we had to fill out,

129
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:13,721
but in a seamless way that does not dilute the original sound.

130
00:10:13,721 --> 00:10:17,862
And also, we often had to balance

131
00:10:17,862 --> 00:10:20,563
gameplay requirements and movie authenticity, which

132
00:10:20,563 --> 00:10:23,863
are not always the same.

