366
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:47,823
Strings in spread voicings or in octaves

367
00:28:47,823 --> 00:28:49,984
to create space or a sense of grandeur.

368
00:28:52,497 --> 00:28:54,559
parallel triads over a pedal bass.

369
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:58,464
In particular, John Williams likes to write a diatonic melody,

370
00:28:58,464 --> 00:29:01,487
but then harmonize it top-down in triads

371
00:29:01,487 --> 00:29:04,670
and move that parallel over a pedal bass movement.

372
00:29:04,670 --> 00:29:08,074
It's a really interesting approach that keeps the ear

